Shortcode that displays a link to the current post's comments. Link and attributes are displayed inside a &lt;span&gt; element.</br>
Supported attributes are <strong>before</strong>, <strong>after</strong>, <strong>span-class</strong>, <strong>span-style</strong>, <strong>link-class</strong>, <strong>link-style</strong>, <strong>no-comments</strong>, <strong>one-comment</strong>, and <strong>more-comments</strong>:

